data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Somerset, KY - a meticulously upgraded haven boasting thoughtful renovations. Hardwood floors guide you to a chef's kitchen with a high-end gas stove, new cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The removal of a wall seamlessly connects the kitchen to the inviting living room. Energy-efficient high-end windows illuminate the space, and a fireplace adds warmth. The journey continues to three tranquil bedrooms on the upper level, offering a private retreat in the master suite.Structurally sound, this home features a 2 car garage, a freshly painted exterior, and a newly added concrete patio. Nestled in a family-friendly subdivision, it's an ideal choice for larger families seeking convenience without compromising on tranquility. Proximity to schools, shopping, and dining establishments adds to the appeal.Don't miss the chance to own this exceptional property - a harmonious blend of sophistication and family-friendly living. Schedule your visit today and witness the allure of this Somerset gem before it becomes someone else's dream home.
